Deity: Demon King Naga
2300px x 2800px PNG
In the third age of Geoda, the Demon Naga was a loyal subject of the Worlokk of the Void. After the Worlokk’s banishment back to the void, Naga took advantage of the power vacuum and became the self appointed Demon King of the Yokai Kingdom where he reigned albeit for a short time.
